import React from 'react';
import './About.css';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';
function About() {
    return (<> 
    <motion.div
        className='background'
        initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
        animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
        exit={{ opacity: 0 }}
        transition={{ duration: 1 }}
      >
    <p id="about"><h1>About Bargain Boutique</h1>

Welcome to Bargain Boutique, your go-to clothing store that believes in representing hope through style in a challenging economy. At Bargain Boutique, we understand that fashion is not just about the latest trends but also about empowering individuals and uplifting communities.

<h2>Our Vision: Hope Through Style</h2>

In a world where economic challenges often restrict access to quality fashion, Bargain Boutique strives to break those barriers. We firmly believe that style should not be limited to a select few but should be inclusive and accessible to all. We are dedicated to offering fashionable clothing and accessories at affordable prices without compromising on quality or style.

<h2>Fashion for All Classes</h2>

While Bargain Boutique specifically caters to those from lower socioeconomic backgrounds, we firmly believe that fashion should be a universal language that transcends social classes. We embrace diversity and aim to create a welcoming space where people from all walks of life can find something unique and special.

<h2>Beyond Mainstream Businesses</h2>

What sets Bargain Boutique apart is our commitment to providing an experience that is truly unmatched by most mainstream businesses. We strive to create an atmosphere where everyone feels valued, respected, and embraced for their individuality. Our team of fashion enthusiasts is passionate about helping you discover your own personal style, regardless of societal norms or constraints.

<h2>Community and Social Impact</h2>

At Bargain Boutique, we believe that fashion can be a catalyst for positive change. We actively engage with our local community, supporting local artists and designers, and promoting sustainable fashion practices. By shopping at Bargain Boutique, you are not only making a style statement but also contributing to a greater cause of building a stronger and more inclusive society.

<h2>Visit Us Today</h2>
We invite you to visit Bargain Boutique and experience the joy of finding stylish and affordable clothing that aligns with your personal taste. Discover a world of fashion where hope, style, and community come together in a harmonious blend. Join us on this fashion journey, where we celebrate individuality and empower you to express yourself through style.

At Bargain Boutique, fashion is more than just a business - it's a movement that represents hope, inclusivity, and the belief that everyone deserves to feel confident and stylish, regardless of their economic circumstances.
<h2 id="contact">Our Contact:</h2>
<p>Phone-number: 778-330-2389</p>
<p>Email:Boutique@virtuesignal.com</p><br />
</p>

</motion.div></>)
}
export default About;
